version_description: The chords are more accurately matched up with the studio version.
Those are the chords for the cover of MCR "Cancer" by "TOP". enjoy :).

I have corrected the chords for the first verse, the instrumental breaks, and the bridge. Mine is also organized into verse/chorus format to make reading easier. I also placed the chords over the lyrics more accurately.
The chord progression for the chorus is incorrect. It outlines the bass bart, but the overall chord isn't right.
I saw this on YouTube and it perfectly ralate to the song.
